    tid = wp.tid()

    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.18 * (v0 + 0.45 - v2 + 0.67)) - (tmp + wp.exp(v0 + 0.93)))
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.33 / tmp + 0.48) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.00)) * ((v0 + 0.06 - v2 + 0.88) / (v0 + 1.00 * v2 + 0.38)))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.12) + (v1 + 0.47 - tmp + 0.47)))
    data[tid] = v0
